User Request (URL in Browser)
   │
   ▼
Routing Engine
   └─> Matches URL → Controller + Action
   │
   ▼
Controller
   └─> Calls Action Method
   └─> Talks to Model (business logic / data)
   │
   ▼
Model
   └─> Interacts with Database / Logic
   └─> Returns data to Controller
   │
   ▼
Controller
   └─> Passes data (Model) to View
   │
   ▼
View (Razor Template)
   └─> Generates HTML
   │
   ▼
Response Back to Browser (Rendered HTML)
